{"tid":369881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國外交國務大臣:不支持港獨","createTime":"2017-08-22T16:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T03:12:48.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80edd44d0d2f7de82d4601af1fa9f2187623fd4c","tid":369881,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:07:16.000Z","msg":"中國外交部長王毅今日在北京會見英國外交國務大臣菲爾德。其中，談及香港的問題時，王毅深入闡述中方立場，而菲爾德則重申，英方在香港問題上堅定支持「一國兩制」，不支持「港獨」。<br />\n<br />\n王毅表示，今年是中英建立大使級外交關係45周年，中方願與英方共同落實好兩國領導人達成的共識，深化「一帶一路」框架內合作，加強在國際和地區問題上的溝通，相互尊重對方核心利益和重大關切，推動中英面向21世紀全球全面戰略夥伴關係深入發展。<br />\n<br />\n菲爾德指出，英國政府高度重視發展對華關係，堅持兩國關係黃金時代的大方向。英方致力於同中方加強貿易、金融、人文、安全等領域合作，支持並積極參與「一帶一路」框架下的合作，願與中方攜手應對全球挑戰，維護世界和平、穩定和發展。<br />\n<br />\n雙方還就北韓核問題、南海問題等交換意見。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1638689/英國外交國務大臣%3A不支持港獨\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F1638689%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%253A%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8&d=a7q6WjsThaM3dk12%2FWXHy%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b6de18f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1638689/英國外交國務大臣%3A不支持港獨</a><br />\n英國政府食屎啦"},{"pid":"80ce55985fa5b25c215f9634e4998e796aa52cf4","tid":369881,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"冇啦冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc2a20213b7fc9604574c257dae6e8d8e1c607d","tid":369881,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇啦冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國狗靠不住"},{"pid":"342f167ee54312392aab7892c6ea519a0308580e","tid":369881,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:15:04.000Z","msg":"英國好想喺「一帶一路」搵到著數。<br />\n人窮志短，國家亦都係咁，<br />\n英國實在係一個沒落中嘅國家，<br />\n你又點可以指望佢做得出乜嘢呢。"},{"pid":"84f9e5b19f688fdfcf77a2367170295397460b58","tid":369881,"uid":17813,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"唔支持港獨嘅話不如收番香港啦"},{"pid":"4e5c030c1254df45185eb54e329f52df9c09058a","tid":369881,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇啦冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國狗靠不住</blockquote><br />\n不嬲都背靠中國支持港獨"},{"pid":"d5b13a26b100cdac01c281825a3e053b3ab2b74f","tid":369881,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:36:21.000Z","msg":"英國欠香港人一個公投呀屌"},{"pid":"4378420532b75346e2191a3ddd9e213e7995176f","tid":369881,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"唔怪得做口交部<br />\n成日幫人含撚"},{"pid":"afa47357e0093960852f9ee921fef2bc2a59de6d","tid":369881,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"佢自己國家都頭痛緊分離主義,點可能會支持香港分離"},{"pid":"df2a74423ef5f512fa435ef5a76329e1fb09f853","tid":369881,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:12:48.000Z","msg":"不嬲最先奶共既係英國<br />\n<br />\n國共內戰結束後<br />\n中英聯合聲明<br />\n到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}